0. Make sure you have python3 and uv installed.
1. run uv sync.
2. Enter your .venv virtual environment (source .venv/bin/activate for Linux/MacOS, .venv\Scripts\activate for Windows.)
3. Run "uv run src/manage.py runserver" and visit http://127.0.0.1:8000/ to access the site.

To migrate database changes: 
    - Navigate to Directory
    - Run "python3 manage.py migrate"